  "title": "Warehouse Assistant",
  "description": "<p><strong>Summary</strong></p><ul><li>Work in a Ecommerce warehouse</li><li>Work Schedule: Option of 5.5 or 6 days work week, 8am to 5pm</li><li>Salary: $2,100 to $2,600</li><li>Location: West</li><li>Singapore Citizen and PR are welcome</li><li>Can converse in English</li><li>Experience with Material Handling Equipment (MHE) is an advantage</li></ul><p><strong>Job Scope</strong></p><ul><li>Receive and QC inbound shipment</li><li>Pick and pack items</li><li>Other basic warehousing tasks including stock count and transfer</li><li>Comfortable standing for long periods during working hours</li><li>Physically fit to handle items up to 12 kg</li></ul><p>If interested, please send your CV to +65 9173 6234 via WhatsApp with the following details:</p><ol><li>Full Name</li><li>Preferred Name (i.e. how to address you)</li><li>Singaporean/PR/non-Singaporean</li><li>Notice Period</li><li>Any Experience in MHE</li></ol>",
